import { Component } from '@angular/core'; import { Patient } from 'src/app/models/Patient'; import { PatientbackService } from 'src/app/services/patientback.service'; @Component({ selector: 'app-list-patient', templateUrl: './list-patient.component.html', styleUrls: ['./list-patient.component.css'] }) export class ListPatientComponent { patients: Patient[] = []; constructor(private patientbackService: PatientbackService) { } ngOnInit(): void { this.patientbackService.getPatient().subscribe( (data: Patient[]) => { this.patients = data; console.log(data); }, (error) => { console.error('Error fetching patients:', error); } ); } }
